{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/06/28/珠海横琴线横穿澳门.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c2bab527-7cb4-5b6e-a034-d16cd14a252b","excerpt":"珠海横琴线横穿澳门 一直没有机会去澳门，疫情期间就更没机会了，不过最近招商游轮开了新航线，从深圳蛇口港到珠海横琴港，中间会横穿澳门，怎么说也算是去过澳门了。 横穿澳门  因为澳门是由澳门半岛和氹仔与路环岛（后面两个岛已经填海连起来了），这次航线就是从澳门这两个岛中间穿过。 招商邮轮疫情期间这个航线单程只要 6…","html":"<h1>珠海横琴线横穿澳门</h1>\n<p>一直没有机会去澳门，疫情期间就更没机会了，不过最近招商游轮开了新航线，从深圳蛇口港到珠海横琴港，中间会横穿澳门，怎么说也算是去过澳门了。</p>\n<h2>横穿澳门</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/4b190/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 105.40540540540542%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/cbe2e/1.webp 148w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/3084c/1.webp 295w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/5ca24/1.webp 590w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/d00b9/1.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/a80bd/1.jpg 148w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/1c91a/1.jpg 295w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/1c72d/1.jpg 590w,\n/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/4b190/1.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/73f4a66663bb08acefd03f0549ab2c1b/1c72d/1.jpg\"\n          alt=\"航线中间经过澳门\"\n          title=\"航线中间经过澳门\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">航线中间经过澳门</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>因为澳门是由澳门半岛和氹仔与路环岛（后面两个岛已经填海连起来了），这次航线就是从澳门这两个岛中间穿过。</p>\n<p>招商邮轮疫情期间这个航线单程只要 65 块钱，于是一大早我便赶到蛇口港登船。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/4b190/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/cbe2e/2.webp 148w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/3084c/2.webp 295w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/5ca24/2.webp 590w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/d00b9/2.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/a80bd/2.jpg 148w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/1c91a/2.jpg 295w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/1c72d/2.jpg 590w,\n/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/4b190/2.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8c9756b64f3ebe8151719db046febde5/1c72d/2.jpg\"\n          alt=\"蛇口港\"\n          title=\"蛇口港\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">蛇口港</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>回头可以看见连接深圳香港的深港大桥，左边是深圳右边是蛇口。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/4b190/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/cbe2e/3.webp 148w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/3084c/3.webp 295w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/5ca24/3.webp 590w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/d00b9/3.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/a80bd/3.jpg 148w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/1c91a/3.jpg 295w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/1c72d/3.jpg 590w,\n/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/4b190/3.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/963fc1b3d5b7eb82d3493d20e45860af/1c72d/3.jpg\"\n          alt=\"深港大桥\"\n          title=\"深港大桥\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">深港大桥</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>途径珠港澳大桥，照片左边金字塔形状的建筑的是珠港澳大桥的人工岛。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/4b190/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.94594594594595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/cbe2e/4.webp 148w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/3084c/4.webp 295w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/5ca24/4.webp 590w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/d00b9/4.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/a80bd/4.jpg 148w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/1c91a/4.jpg 295w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/1c72d/4.jpg 590w,\n/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/4b190/4.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/7df417b7b4683b67dc1193f93ad5bcfc/1c72d/4.jpg\"\n          alt=\"珠港澳大桥人工岛\"\n          title=\"珠港澳大桥人工岛\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">珠港澳大桥人工岛</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>因为疫情关系，珠三角间的健康码还没能互通，大桥上面一辆车都没有。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/4b190/5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/cbe2e/5.webp 148w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/3084c/5.webp 295w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/5ca24/5.webp 590w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/d00b9/5.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/a80bd/5.jpg 148w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/1c91a/5.jpg 295w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/1c72d/5.jpg 590w,\n/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/4b190/5.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f9718e703185944de94c5602a435279b/1c72d/5.jpg\"\n          alt=\"珠港澳大桥\"\n          title=\"珠港澳大桥\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">珠港澳大桥</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>途径的海岛架满风车用于发电。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/4b190/6.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/cbe2e/6.webp 148w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/3084c/6.webp 295w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/5ca24/6.webp 590w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/d00b9/6.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/a80bd/6.jpg 148w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/1c91a/6.jpg 295w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/1c72d/6.jpg 590w,\n/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/4b190/6.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/2eede37b89a56aac5b041bd25ae9fef2/1c72d/6.jpg\"\n          alt=\"风车\"\n          title=\"风车\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">风车</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>大概一小时左右，船驶入澳门，此时已经能收到澳门的短信了，但是广播要求最好不要打开漫游，以避免影响到健康码。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/4b190/7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/cbe2e/7.webp 148w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/3084c/7.webp 295w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/5ca24/7.webp 590w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/d00b9/7.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/a80bd/7.jpg 148w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/1c91a/7.jpg 295w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/1c72d/7.jpg 590w,\n/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/4b190/7.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/70f76e43b8d262681169e4f933023751/1c72d/7.jpg\"\n          alt=\"澳门塔\"\n          title=\"澳门塔\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">澳门塔</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/4b190/8.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.432432432432435%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/cbe2e/8.webp 148w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/3084c/8.webp 295w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/5ca24/8.webp 590w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/d00b9/8.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/a80bd/8.jpg 148w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/1c91a/8.jpg 295w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/1c72d/8.jpg 590w,\n/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/4b190/8.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a1dd9392698b1c6c8a3555b3a116262a/1c72d/8.jpg\"\n          alt=\"澳门塔和新葡京\"\n          title=\"澳门塔和新葡京\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">澳门塔和新葡京</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>澳门的葡式建筑很有特色，比如下面的 8 字摩天轮。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/4b190/9.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/cbe2e/9.webp 148w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/3084c/9.webp 295w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/5ca24/9.webp 590w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/d00b9/9.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/a80bd/9.jpg 148w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/1c91a/9.jpg 295w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/1c72d/9.jpg 590w,\n/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/4b190/9.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/4885a69cdfb52e5a1f2bc9adac5817d7/1c72d/9.jpg\"\n          alt=\"8字摩天轮\"\n          title=\"8字摩天轮\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">8字摩天轮</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>到达横琴港看澳门那边，和香港差不多的是，澳门也把最不发达的地方面向大陆。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\