yle=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/4b190/11.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/cbe2e/11.webp 148w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/3084c/11.webp 295w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/5ca24/11.webp 590w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/d00b9/11.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/a80bd/11.jpg 148w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/1c91a/11.jpg 295w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/1c72d/11.jpg 590w,\n/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/4b190/11.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/d37a4308db6544ce7838ae94d1c8e8a1/1c72d/11.jpg\"\n          alt=\"钟楼\"\n          title=\"钟楼\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">钟楼</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/4b190/12.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/cbe2e/12.webp 148w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/3084c/12.webp 295w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/5ca24/12.webp 590w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/d00b9/12.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/a80bd/12.jpg 148w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/1c91a/12.jpg 295w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/1c72d/12.jpg 590w,\n/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/4b190/12.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/5581d19c9dce01704054f17617511d01/1c72d/12.jpg\"\n          alt=\"港口\"\n          title=\"港口\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">港口</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/4b190/13.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/cbe2e/13.webp 148w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/3084c/13.webp 295w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/5ca24/13.webp 590w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/d00b9/13.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/a80bd/13.jpg 148w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/1c91a/13.jpg 295w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/1c72d/13.jpg 590w,\n/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/4b190/13.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/01500aefa615ddd720ea2ad1e6a9fdcc/1c72d/13.jpg\"\n          alt=\"我\"\n          title=\"我\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">我</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>尴尬的地方是这个港口非常小，小到连一个公共厕所都没有，最近的厕所也要 500m 左右。</p>\n<h2>长隆</h2>\n<p>横琴是珠海比较欠发达的地方，几乎除了长隆就没什么可以提的地方了，从横琴到珠海市区或者机场都要到长隆乘坐旅游巴士，而且这两个地方的买票地点不一样。景区的工作人员会带你去前往市区的买票点，去机场的买票点则在各种酒店（企鹅酒店或者马戏酒店），在微信搜索珠海机场快线也能预定车票。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/4b190/14.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/cbe2e/14.webp 148w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/3084c/14.webp 295w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/5ca24/14.webp 590w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/d00b9/14.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/a80bd/14.jpg 148w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/1c91a/14.jpg 295w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/1c72d/14.jpg 590w,\n/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/4b190/14.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/4662b0c37078fe9c20cfd1bf5fe174c3/1c72d/14.jpg\"\n          alt=\"长隆\"\n          title=\"长隆\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">长隆</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/4b190/15.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/cbe2e/15.webp 148w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/3084c/15.webp 295w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/5ca24/15.webp 590w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/d00b9/15.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/a80bd/15.jpg 148w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/1c91a/15.jpg 295w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/1c72d/15.jpg 590w,\n/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/4b190/15.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/25896dbad0c1b40576dd3a44920188d3/1c72d/15.jpg\"\n          alt=\"长隆马戏酒店\"\n          title=\"长隆马戏酒店\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">长隆马戏酒店</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/28/珠海横琴线横穿澳门.html","date":"June 28, 2020","title":"珠海横琴线横穿澳门"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/28/珠海横琴线横穿澳门.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/南山博物馆浮世绘展.html","title":"南山博物馆浮世绘展"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}},"next":null}}}